{%- comment -%}
  Dynamic Collection Hero & Tabbed Content Section
  Pulls data from collection metafields for a premium, custom experience.
  Also supports hardcoded content for specific collection handles.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- assign lifestyle_img = collection.metafields.custom.lifestyle_image -%}
{%- assign gem_icon = collection.metafields.custom.gem_icon -%}
{%- assign summary = collection.metafields.custom.summary_text | default: collection.description -%}
{%- assign benefits = collection.metafields.custom.quick_benefits -%}

{%- comment -%} Enhanced Fallbacks for "Empty" collections {%- endcomment -%}
{%- if benefits == blank -%}
  {%- assign benefits = "Premium Certified Gemstones\nEnergized & Lab-Tested\n7-Day Easy Returns" -%}
{%- endif -%}

{%- comment -%} ========== Hardcoded content for specific collections ========== {%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign gem_handle = collection.handle -%}

{%- comment -%} Blue Sapphire hero overrides {%- endcomment -%}
{%- if gem_handle == 'blue-sapphire' -%}
  {%- assign hero_tagline = 'नीलम — Where Stillness Becomes Strength' -%}
  {%- if collection.metafields.custom.summary_text == blank -%}
    {%- assign summary = 'Some stones are made to be seen. नीलम महसूस करने के लिए है. It does not dazzle — it settles, like certainty, like the moment doubt leaves the room. यह रत्न उनके लिए है जो बिना शोर के नेतृत्व करते हैं — जो धैर्य से बनाते हैं, जल्दी से नहीं।' -%}
  {%- endif -%}
  {%- if collection.metafields.custom.quick_benefits == blank -%}
    {%- assign benefits = 'Certified Natural\nTreatment Fully Disclosed\nNo Glass or Diffusion Filling' -%}
  {%- endif -%}
{%- endif -%}

{%- capture mapped_about -%}
  {%- case gem_handle -%}
    {%- when 'emerald' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p><em>Emerald does not demand attention. It settles the mind.</em></p>
        <p>Emerald (Panna) is chosen not for display but for what it organises beneath it — clearer thinking, steadier speech, and perception that sharpens naturally. Known as Panna, Pachu, Maragatham, Marakatha, or Zamrud, it is associated with ☿ Budh (Mercury) for clarity, wisdom, and steady communication.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">पन्ना — स्थिर बुद्धि और स्पष्ट सोच का रत्न</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">☿ बुध ग्रह से जुड़ा यह रत्न बुद्धि, संचार और विवेक को स्थिर करता है। पन्ना — गहराई, स्पष्ट सोच और संयमित अभिव्यक्ति का रत्न।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> ☿ Budh (Mercury)</p>
        <p><strong>Governs:</strong> Intellect, communication, memory, analysis, and discernment</p>
        <p>Wearing Emerald is not about speeding the mind up — it is about refining it. When Mercury is balanced, thought flows with clarity and composure: decisions become steadier, speech becomes more precise, and perception sharpens naturally. Best suited for students, professionals, traders, writers, analysts, and advisors — anyone whose work lives or dies on the quality of their thinking and expression.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Certified Natural &nbsp;·&nbsp; Stable Heat Treatment &nbsp;·&nbsp; No Chemical Filling</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    {%- when 'blue-sapphire' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p>Blue Sapphire (Neelam) is not a stone that dazzles — it settles, like certainty, like the moment doubt leaves the room. Ruled by ♄ Shani (Saturn), it anchors the wearer in discipline, resilience, and grounded authority. Known as Neelam, Neelamani, or Shani Ratna, it is worn by those who build without noise and lead without hurry.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">नीलम — Where Stillness Becomes Strength</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">नीलम महसूस करने के लिए है। यह रत्न उनके लिए है जो बिना शोर के नेतृत्व करते हैं — जो धैर्य से बनाते हैं, जल्दी से नहीं।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> ♄ Shani (Saturn)</p>
        <p><strong>Governs:</strong> Discipline, responsibility, justice, stability, and long-term growth</p>
        <p>Blue Sapphire aligns with Saturn's energy — supporting focus, resilience, and steady progress. It encourages clarity, discipline, and grounded decision-making. Helps reduce confusion, fear, and scattered thinking, replacing it with structure and composure. Best suited for those carrying serious responsibility and building toward long-term success.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Certified Natural &nbsp;·&nbsp; Treatment Fully Disclosed &nbsp;·&nbsp; No Glass or Diffusion Filling</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    {%- when 'opal' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p><em>Opal is not a single colour. It is living light in motion.</em></p>
        <p>Opal (Doodhiya Patthar) is linked to ♀ Shukra (Venus) for beauty, harmony, creativity, and quiet confidence. It restores self-worth when confidence has quietly eroded, softens emotional turbulence, and opens the creative channels that Venus naturally governs.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">ओपल — जहाँ रंग साँस लेते हैं</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">ओपल --- जहाँ रंग ठहरते नहीं, बस हर झलक में बदलते हैं। ♀ शुक्र से जुड़ा यह रत्न सौंदर्य, आनंद और भावनात्मक संतुलन लौटाता है।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> ♀ Shukra (Venus)</p>
        <p><strong>Governs:</strong> Beauty, harmony, relationships, creativity, comfort, and refined pleasures</p>
        <p>Venus is the planet of what makes life feel worth living — connection, elegance, joy, and ease. Opal is worn to invite more of that energy in. For those who feel disconnected from pleasure, beauty, or warmth in their relationships, Opal works as a gentle but consistent realignment. It is well suited to artists, designers, performers, creative professionals, and anyone navigating the emotional landscape of relationships.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Certified Natural &nbsp;·&nbsp; Untreated &amp; Uncoated &nbsp;·&nbsp; No Doublets, Triplets, Wax, or Resin</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    {%- when 'ruby' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p><em>Ruby does not whisper. It ignites.</em></p>
        <p>Ruby (Manikya) is ruled by ☉ Surya (Sun), worn for strength, vitality, courage, and self-authority. Known as Manikya, Manik, or the King of Gems, it is chosen when strength must rise with clarity and conviction — not to dominate others, but to stop diminishing yourself.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">माणिक — अग्नि, शक्ति और आत्मबल का रत्न</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">माणिक छुपता नहीं --- यह भीतर की अग्नि को जागृत करता है। ☉ सूर्य से जुड़ा यह रत्न साहस, स्पष्टता और नेतृत्व को प्रबल करता है।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> ☉ Surya (Sun)</p>
        <p><strong>Governs:</strong> Vitality, authority, self-worth, leadership, courage, and life force</p>
        <p>The Sun is the source. Ruby strengthens confidence when it has quietly dimmed, restores decisiveness when self-doubt has taken hold, and brings the clarity of direction that comes from knowing who you are and what you stand for. Best suited to leaders, entrepreneurs, executives, public figures, administrators, and anyone whose role demands presence, conviction, and the ability to act with authority.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Certified Natural &nbsp;·&nbsp; Treatment Fully Disclosed &nbsp;·&nbsp; No Glass or Lead Filling</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    {%- when 'yellow-sapphire' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p><em>Yellow Sapphire is not brightness that overwhelms. It is light that guides.</em></p>
        <p>Yellow Sapphire (Pukhraj) is ruled by ♃ Guru (Jupiter) — worn for wisdom, clarity, meaningful growth, and steady prosperity. Known as Pukhraj, Pushparag, or Peetmani, it brings optimism that is grounded rather than reckless, and prosperity that is built rather than stumbled into.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">पुखराज — ज्ञान और मार्गदर्शन का रत्न</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">पुखराज चकाचौंध नहीं करता --- यह सही दिशा दिखाता है। ♃ गुरु (बृहस्पति) से जुड़ा यह रत्न ज्ञान, स्पष्टता और सही दिशा धीरे-धीरे प्रकट करता है।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> ♃ Guru (Jupiter)</p>
        <p><strong>Governs:</strong> Wisdom, learning, prosperity, judgment, ethics, and long-term growth</p>
        <p>Jupiter is the planet of understanding — not just knowledge, but the discernment to use it well. Yellow Sapphire brings that quality into sharper focus: clearer thinking, more guided decisions, and the confidence that comes from genuine understanding. Well suited to students, teachers, advisors, consultants, professionals, and spiritual seekers whose work depends on judgment and depth.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Certified Natural &nbsp;·&nbsp; Treatment Fully Disclosed &nbsp;·&nbsp; No Glass or Diffusion Filling</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    {%- when 'white-sapphire' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p>White Sapphire (Safed Pukhraj) represents harmony and composed light. Ruled by ♀ Shukra (Venus), it allows inner alignment and discernment to arrive in their own time. Known as Safed Pukhraj or Colourless Sapphire, it creates balance without demanding attention.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">🤍 सफ़ेद पुखराज — प्रकाश में ठहरा हुआ संतुलन</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">सफ़ेद पुखराज दिखावा नहीं करता, यह भीतर की स्पष्टता और गरिमा को धीरे-धीरे प्रकट करता है। जो रत्न आपके लिए है, वही संतुलन महसूस कराएगा।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> ♀ Shukra (Venus) | <strong>Zodiac:</strong> ♉ Taurus, ♎ Libra</p>
      </div>
    {%- when 'red-coral' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p>Red Coral (Moonga) represents steadied fire and resilience. Ruled by ♂ Mangal (Mars), it builds willpower and restores confidence without agitation. Known as Moonga, Pagadam, or Pravala, it is chosen when energy seeks direction rather than provocation.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">🤍 लाल मूंगा — संतुलित शक्ति का प्रतीक</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">♂ मंगल से जुड़ा यह रत्न तब चुना जाता है जब ऊर्जा को दिशा चाहिए — उग्रता की नहीं। यह शक्ति और नियंत्रण दोनों को समेटे रहता है।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> ♂ Mangal (Mars) | <strong>Zodiac:</strong> ♈ Aries, ♏ Scorpio</p>
      </div>
    {%- when 'pearl' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p>Pearl (Moti) represents serenity and emotional balance. Ruled by 🌙 Chandra (Moon), it restores mental peace and gentle clarity. Known as Moti or Mukta, Pearl carries the quiet grace of the moon, soothing the mind and heart.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">🤍 मोती — चंद्रमा की शांति का रूप</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">चंद्रमा से जुड़ा यह रत्न मन, भावनाओं और भीतर की स्थिरता को धीरे-धीरे संतुलित करता है। जहाँ बेचैनी हो, वहाँ यह शांति बनकर उतरता है।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> 🌙 Chandra (Moon) | <strong>Zodiac:</strong> ♋ Cancer</p>
      </div>
    {%- when 'hessonite' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p>Hessonite (Gomed) represents grounded fire and discernment. Ruled by ☊ Rahu, it steadies perception and grounds restless energy. Known as Gomed, Gomedak, or Cinnamon Stone, it brings clarity when paths feel blurred or influences feel misleading.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">🤍 गोमेद — भ्रम को स्पष्टता में बदलने वाला रत्न</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">☊ राहु से जुड़ा यह रत्न तब चुना जाता है जब जीवन में गति तो हो, पर दिशा अस्पष्ट लगे। यह भ्रम को हटाकर सत्य को सामने लाता है।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> ☊ Rahu | <strong>Zodiac:</strong> ♒ Aquarius, ♏ Scorpio</p>
      </div>
    {%- when 'cats-eye' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p>Cat’s Eye (Lehsunia) represents visible focus and protective precision. Ruled by ☋ Ketu, it cuts through distraction and dissolves illusion. Known as Lehsunia, Lahsuniya, or Vaidurya, the soul of this gem is chatoyancy—a living line of light.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">🤍 लेहसुनिया — जब एकाग्रता दिखाई देने लगे</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">☋ केतु से जुड़ा यह रत्न भ्रम नहीं बढ़ाता — उसे हटा देता है। यह रत्न तब चुना जाता है जब मन को फैलाव नहीं, एकाग्रता चाहिए।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> ☋ Ketu | <strong>Zodiac:</strong> ♏ Scorpio, ♐ Sagittarius</p>
      </div>
    {%- when 'amethyst' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p>Amethyst (Jamuniya) represents stillness and insight. A gentler alternative to Blue Sapphire, it is linked to ♄ Shani (Saturn) and chosen when mental order is needed without intensity. Known as Jamuniya or Katela, it settles the mind and steadies thought.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">🤍 जमुनिया (अमेथिस्ट / कटेला) — शांति और संतुलन का रत्न</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">यह रत्न शनि से जुड़ा माना जाता है और नीलम का सौम्य विकल्प समझा जाता है। वह मन को ठहराव देता है और स्पष्टता को अपने समय पर आने देता है।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> ♄ Shani (Saturn) | <strong>Zodiac:</strong> ♒ Aquarius, ♑ Capricorn</p>
      </div>
    {%- when 'citrine' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p>Citrine (Sunela) represents light and growth. Linked to ♃ Guru (Jupiter), it illuminates quietly, supporting confidence and prosperity. Known as Citrine, Sunela, or Golden Quartz, it reflects an inner brightness that unfolds naturally without pressure.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">🤍 सिट्रीन (सुनैला) — सौम्य प्रकाश में बढ़ता विकास</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">♃ गुरु (बृहस्पति) से जुड़ा यह रत्न ज्ञान, विवेक और समृद्धि को स्वाभाविक गति से आगे बढ़ाता है। जो सुनैला आपके लिए है, वही स्पष्टता देगा।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> ♃ Guru (Jupiter) | <strong>Zodiac:</strong> ♐ Sagittarius, ♓ Pisces</p>
      </div>
    {%- when 'turquoise' -%}
      <div class="gem-about">
        <p>Turquoise (Firoza) represents reassuring protection and skystone calm. Associated with ♃ Guru (Jupiter) and ♀ Shukra (Venus), it brings emotional ease and steady movement. Known as Firoza or Firouzeh, it is one of humanity’s oldest protective talismans.</p>
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 25px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">🤍 फिरोज़ा — आकाश की शांति, धरती की सुरक्षा</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0;">फिरोज़ा वह रत्न है जिसमें आकाश और धरती साथ ठहरते हैं। यह रत्न भारी नहीं पड़ता — यह सहारा देता है। जो फिरोज़ा आपके लिए है, वही सुकून देगा।</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Planet:</strong> ♃ Guru (Jupiter), ♀ Shukra (Venus)</p>
      </div>
  {%- endcase -%}
{%- endcapture -%}

