    {%- when 'ruby' -%}
      <p>Ruby is for those whose roles require visibility, responsibility, and conviction. It restores inner authority — not by forcing strength, but by removing what was dimming it.</p>
      <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin: 20px 0;">
        <strong>Best Suited For:</strong>
