{%- capture mapped_care_guide -%}
  {%- case gem_handle -%}
    {%- when 'emerald' -%}
      <p>Emerald has a delicate internal structure. It is not fragile — but it is alive with natural character, and it responds best to gentleness.</p>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-top: 16px;">
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
          <h4 style="color: #1a3c34; margin-bottom: 10px;">✅ Do's</h4>
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li>Wipe with a soft cloth after wear.</li>
            <li>Clean occasionally with lukewarm water and a drop of mild soap.</li>
            <li>Store separately in a padded box.</li>
            <li>Apply a light, colourless oil only if advised.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #fff5f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
          <h4 style="color: #c53030; margin-bottom: 10px;">❌ Don'ts</h4>
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li>Avoid heat, steam, and sudden temperature changes.</li>
            <li>Keep away from chemicals, perfumes, detergents, and alcohol-based products.</li>
            <li>Never use ultrasonic cleaning — it strips stabilising oils.</li>
            <li>Remove during physical activity or manual work.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 16px; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold); margin-top: 20px;">
        <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>On treatments:</strong> Light to moderate oiling is a globally accepted, traditional practice — and it is always disclosed on certification. Heavy resin or polymer filling is never acceptable. Visible oil seepage is a red flag and should be avoided.</p>
      </div>
    {%- when 'blue-sapphire' -%}
      <p>Blue Sapphire is one of the hardest gemstones in the world — Mohs 9 — which makes it naturally well-suited to daily wear. That said, mindful care keeps it at its best over years of use.</p>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-top: 16px;">
        <div style="background: #fdfaf5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
          <h4 style="color: #1a3c34; margin-bottom: 10px;">✅ Do's</h4>
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li>Clean gently with a soft cloth after wear.</li>
            <li>Use lukewarm water and a drop of mild soap occasionally.</li>
            <li>Store separately in a padded box away from harder stones.</li>
            <li>Ensure the setting is secure before wearing regularly.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #fff5f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
          <h4 style="color: #c53030; margin-bottom: 10px;">❌ Don'ts</h4>
          <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li>Avoid chemicals, perfumes, and detergents.</li>
            <li>Do not use ultrasonic or steam cleaning.</li>
            <li>Keep away from extreme heat and prolonged direct sunlight.</li>
            <li>Remove during heavy physical activity, gym, or contact sports.</li>
          </ul>
